            , and desired him<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="178410200117"></xptr> to bring it, it was sold to Mr. Sammon in the Strand.</p>
               <p>Court. The production of the watch is extremely material.</p>
               <p>(
               <persName id="t17841020-70-person721">
                  Judah
                   Levy
