                  </persName>
             sold his commission? - That I do not know.</p>
               <p>Did you ever know him in the army? - I cannot say that I perfectly know it.</p>
               <p>Is he a navy captain? - That I do not know, he was in the Custom-house I know, I never knew him by any other name than Mr. Freeman.</p>
